00:39:03,190 --> 00:39:07,410
Rym: Are they easy to use if you understand networking and basic system administration?

663
00:39:07,830 --> 00:39:08,725
Scott: Well, sort of, right?

664
00:39:08,746 --> 00:39:12,618
Scott: I mean, you know, I'm not going to just be a salesman for Amazon here.

665
00:39:12,638 --> 00:39:13,770
Scott: There are some problems, right?

666
00:39:13,850 --> 00:39:17,210
Scott: The major problem they have is that they have this web interface, the console.

