00:40:02,216 --> 00:40:09,740
Scott: I think there's a Firefox extension with a GUI for S3, and Ubuntu has Ubuntu Landscape you can use to manage a group of Ubuntu servers.

681
00:40:11,170 --> 00:40:18,018
