00:41:48,279 --> 00:41:48,380
Scott: up.".

705
00:41:49,027 --> 00:41:49,330
Scott: Right?

706
00:41:49,430 --> 00:41:50,704
Scott: It's like, "What do you mean?

707
00:41:50,765 --> 00:41:52,745
Scott: the hardware broke that my machine was on?

708
00:41:52,786 --> 00:41:53,674
Scott: It's a virtual machine!

709
00:41:53,695 --> 00:41:54,725
Scott: Fucking move it live!

710
00:41:54,785 --> 00:41:55,250
Scott: Zen can do

