721
00:42:34,527 --> 00:42:36,430
Scott: It doesn't monitor everything you want it to monitor.

722
00:42:36,912 --> 00:42:40,510
Scott: And it doesn't monitor it so quickly, even if you pay for the detailed monitoring.

723
00:42:41,012 --> 00:42:46,630
Scott: It's like once a minute, you know, so you're gonna lose some minutes, right, if you're relying on CloudWatch.

