763
00:45:02,950 --> 00:45:05,410
Rym: And you can run a lot at the same time on a Zen server.

764
00:45:05,511 --> 00:45:12,750
Rym: But I don't need a gigantic hunk of hardware capable of doing all this for the four times a year that something's released.

